description: The yellow brick road has never been this thrilling. Inspired by the film Oz the Great and Powerful, Temple Run: Oz combines the legendary endless running gameplay of Temple Run 2 with the breathtaking landscapes of the Land of Oz. Reimagined for the Windows 8 Modern UI, this title offers an immersive, high-definition experience that takes the franchise to new heights.
